Game Data Installation
======================

To run Ultima 7, place the respective extracted files for The Black Gate and
Serpent Isle into ${TRUEPREFIX}/share/exult/{blackgate,serpentisle},
respectively.

Audio packs (all-in-one or separate) are needed to play sound effects and music
other than MIDI. They are available under the Download section of
${HOMEPAGE}.
